   "source": [
    "# Direct GPQR\n",
    "\n",
    "In this example, the data generating process is\n",
    "$$Y = \\cos(2 \\pi (X+0.1)) + \\epsilon, \\quad \\epsilon \\sim \\mathcal{N}(0, X+0.1),$$\n",
    "and quantile functions $Q_{\\tau_i}(x)$ of residuals are modeled by linear combination of latent GP $g_j(x)$."
   ]
